about_us_text: In accordance with the Resolution of the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan dated October 10, 2023 No. 329 'On measures for the radical reform of the railway transport sector' and the Order of the Chairman of 'Uzbekiston temir yo'llari' JSC dated November 10, 2023 No. 897, 'Temiryo'lekspress' Joint-Stock Company was established. The company provides technical-technological support and passenger service for six high-speed Afrosiyob electric trains.
